channel.title: Clickingmost teleports?
channel.description:
my 317 source doesnt have a clicking most. does anyone know where else the teles would be at? im trying to change the ones in the emotes tab. and when i click on one of the teleports, home for example. it'll send a message saying you teleport to home. so i opened client.java and typed "you teleport to home" and the only thing it found was if i do the command ::home. so i searched the whole folder and it brought up client.java npcHandler.java and items.txt
i opened each one and searched for "you teleport home" and none of them found it except client.java which was ::home. should i just get a new source or where do i look? im sure its somewhere or else the emotes tabs wouldnt have teleports in the first place. i also looked for action buttons and didnt find it.
